data.text:
UPDATE: Helicopter has arrived dropping water on the #HollisterFire. 
200 acres, 10 contained. Winds are gusty. Dozens of homes on Hollister Ranch have been put under an evacuation warning. Team coverage continues on @KEYTNC3 @KCOY @KKFXFox11 with @AlysMartinezTV and @JasonStiff. https://t.co/2fSnTshGNm
